39:05.960 --> 39:07.564
See how it feels.

39:09.720 --> 39:10.721
[Dion] Huh?

39:13.640 --> 39:14.687
Yeah.

39:15.040 --> 39:17.088
[sniffles]

39:19.360 --> 39:20.600
