Five days.

39:34.040 --> 39:35.041
All right.

39:41.520 --> 39:42.567
[chuckles]

39:43.520 --> 39:46.524
[slow-tempo bluegrass plays]

40:01.600 --> 40:03.170
I had a bad day.

40:04.200 --> 40:05.326
That's no excuse.

40:06.200 --> 40:09.329
Should never have
yelled at you like that, okay?

40:11.360 --> 40:12.805
I'm really sorry.

40:13.080 --> 40:16.880
[slow-tempo guitar plays]

40:18.360 --> 40:21.204
[sighs]

40:25.040 --> 40:27.486
You accept my apology, hmm?

40:55.280 --> 40:56.520
