41:05.160 --> 41:07.288
Stylin'. Oh, that's me and Dion.

41:07.480 --> 41:10.768
I was, uh--
actually, I was about your age.

41:13.320 --> 41:16.244
[slow-tempo guitar plays]

41:23.440 --> 41:25.044
Love your hair.

41:25.120 --> 41:26.167
[laughs]

41:27.600 --> 41:30.410
Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.
Jets and Giants.

